OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FFrom rising costs to the turmoil in
OL,6,Fthe Middle East, the holiday market is
OL,7,Fproving particularly hard to navigate
OL,8,Fthis year. In this week's episode of
OL,9,FTonight, Charlotte Hawkins finds out
OL,10,Fwhat this all means for your next
OL,11,Fgetaway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
