PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777558268
OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FIn recent months, some British
OL,6,Fholidaymakers found themselves in the
OL,7,Feye of the storm as international
OL,8,Funrest escalated. Tonight spoke to
OL,9,FLee, who was in Dubai when conflict
OL,10,Fspread across the Middle East after
OL,11,Fthe United States and Israel launched
OL,12,Fstrikes on Iran on February 28. One
OL,13,Fmorning, while he was in the pool at
OL,14,Fhis hotel, he heard missiles flying
OL,15,Foverhead while he was in the pool at
OL,16,Fhis hotel.
OL,18,F"It was just so high in the air, and
OL,19,Fso loud and fast, it was just
OL,20,Fsomething that was alien." - Lee
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777558268
OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FLee made it home safe. But stories
OL,6,Flike his have made some people look
OL,7,Fagain at their travel plans.
OL,9,FNicole has booked the holiday of a
OL,10,Flifetime to a resort in Turkey in May.
OL,11,FIt's the first holiday she has booked
OL,12,Fwith her children, and she hasn't been
OL,13,Fabroad for 15 years. But with one eye
OL,14,Fon the ongoing situation in the
OL,15,Fregion, Nicole has been getting
OL,16,Fnervous.
OL,18,F"What if things escalate? What if we
OL,19,Fget stuck? Being stuck abroad is
OL,20,Fpetrifying, especially with two young
OL,21,Fchildren." - Nicole
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777558268
OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FPart of the reason for Nicole's
OL,6,Fconcern is the recent experience of
OL,7,Fher sister-in-law Kim, who was on her
OL,8,Fhoneymoon in Thailand when the Iran
OL,9,Fwar began. She was due to fly home via
OL,10,FDoha, Qatar, but the disruption meant
OL,11,Fthat her flight was cancelled, leading
OL,12,Fto a rushed effort to find an
OL,13,Falternative route back.
OL,15,F"I cried because I just thought now
OL,16,FI've got to try and get home and I
OL,17,Fcan't enjoy it like I really wanted
OL,18,Fto. So I was gutted." - Kim
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777558268
OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FKim did eventually find a way home,
OL,6,Fvia an extra flight and extended
OL,7,Fwaiting at airports, but it put a
OL,8,Fdampener on her trip.
OL,10,FTo get a view from the ground, Tonight
OL,11,Finvited social media influencer Sharon
OL,12,F- also known as @yourlassieinturkiye -
OL,13,Fto visit Nicole to offer her
OL,14,Fperspective as someone who lives in
OL,15,FTurkey.
OL,17,FWhile she told Nicole that 'life is
OL,18,Fcompletely normal in Turkey' at the
OL,19,Fmoment, Sharon advised those
OL,20,Ftravelling there to check the latest
OL,21,FFCDO travel advice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777558268
OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FTonight also met aviation analyst John
OL,6,FGrant, who said the current airspace
OL,7,Fdisruption was 'unprecedented'.
OL,9,FAnd the closure of the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz, a vital shipping route for oil
OL,11,Fand gas, has caused the price of
OL,12,Frefined products like jet fuel to
OL,13,Fsurge - and that ultimately means
OL,14,Fhigher costs for passengers.
OL,16,F"Prices have already risen this year,
OL,17,Fbut we haven't seen the end of it.
OL,18,FTravellers will be paying more over
OL,19,Fthe coming months." - Paul Charles,
OL,20,FAviation and Travel Expert
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
