PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777558268
OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FThe turbulence around the globe has
OL,6,Fled to a surge in interest in UK
OL,7,Fstaycations, with some operators
OL,8,Freporting sharply increased bookings.
OL,9,FHolidaymaker Andrew says a UK holiday
OL,10,Favoids any of the potential
OL,11,Fcomplexities of going abroad when
OL,12,Fthings feel unstable.
OL,14,F"If I was to go to Cyprus, Turkey etc,
OL,15,FI might be a bit more worried, but
OL,16,Fgoing to the UK, you know exactly what
OL,17,Fyou're going to get, and I do feel
OL,18,Fsafe, and I feel safe for my wife and
OL,19,Fmy family as well." - Andrew
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777558268
OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FClaire Flower, director of Beverley
OL,6,FHolidays in Devon, said they have seen
OL,7,Fa surge in bookings at the moment. But
OL,8,Fdespite this increase, she sees
OL,9,Fchallenges ahead for UK tourism
OL,10,Foperators, with rising bills and the
OL,11,Fpossibility of tourism taxes being
OL,12,Fintroduced in England.
OL,14,FDefenders of the idea say it would
OL,15,Fhelp to raise funds for local
OL,16,Finfrastructure, tourism promotion and
OL,17,Fpublic services.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
