SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777558268
OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FAn EU system designed to track every
OL,6,Fnon-EU traveller entering the Schengen
OL,7,FArea - replacing passport stamps with
OL,8,Fbiometric checks - has now also gone
OL,9,Flive. But the process has been blamed
OL,10,Ffor long delays at European airports,
OL,11,Fand some passengers have missed
OL,12,Fflights entirely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
