PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777558268
OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FThe European Commission told Tonight
OL,6,Fthat Europe now has the most modern IT
OL,7,Fborder system in the world. They said
OL,8,Fthe "core purpose is to make our
OL,9,Fborders more secure and protect EU
OL,10,Fcitizens, and we are already seeing
OL,11,Fvery good results. In the overwhelming
OL,12,Fmajority of Member States there are no
OL,13,Fissues and the commission remains in
OL,14,Fclose contact with them."
OL,26,@pD@EOUvD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
