OL,3,CHoliday Havoc: Where Should You Go?
OL,5,FDespite the disruption, this holiday
OL,6,Fseason plenty of trips will go ahead
OL,7,Fas planned, and the most recent
OL,8,Findications are that Turkey and Cyprus
OL,9,Fare on track for a strong recovery-
OL,10,F and there could be some bargains to
OL,11,Fbe had.
OL,13,FUseful links:
OL,15,FCheck the latest FCDO travel advice at
OL,16,Fhttps://www.gov.uk/foreign-travel-
OL,17,Fadvice
OL,19,FFor details on claiming compensation
OL,20,Fif your holiday has been disrupted,
OL,21,Fvisit Citizens Advice
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
